  "title": "Haulage Transport Coordinator",
  "description": "<h2>Role Overview:</h2><p>We are seeking a Haulage Transport Coordinator to manage and coordinate daily transport operations. This role ensures timely movement of containers and cargo, effective communication with drivers and customers, and smooth execution of haulage activities.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>• Plan and coordinate daily haulage schedules and truck deployment</p><p>• Liaise with drivers, customers, port terminals, and depot operators</p><p>• Monitor truck movements and ensure on-time delivery</p><p>• Prepare transport documentation and job orders</p><p>• Handle customer inquiries and resolve delivery issues</p><p>• Ensure compliance with safety and transport regulations</p><p>• Update transport system and maintain accurate records</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>• Experience in haulage, transport, or logistics operations preferred</p><p>• Familiarity with Singapore port/terminal operations is an advantage</p><p>• Good coordination and communication skills</p><p>• Able to work under pressure and manage multiple jobs</p><p>• Proficient in MS Office / transport management systems<br /></p><p><em>Notes : Working location will be at Keppel Distripark</em></p>",
